@startuml Admin_Approve
title Admin Approve Verification Sequence Diagram

actor Admin
participant "Frontend" as FE
participant "API Gateway" as API
participant "Admin Controller" as Ctrl
database "Database" as DB
participant "Security Log" as Log

Admin -> FE: Request to approve verification
activate FE
FE -> API: POST /admin/approve
activate API
API -> Ctrl: Forward request
activate Ctrl

Ctrl -> DB: Update verification status
activate DB
DB --> Ctrl: Success
deactivate DB

Ctrl -> Log: IP & Action logging
activate Log
Log --> Ctrl: Acknowledged
deactivate Log

Ctrl --> API: Approved (200 OK)
deactivate Ctrl
API --> FE: Success Response
deactivate API
FE --> Admin: Show success message
deactivate FE

@enduml
